    "We advocate for aligning publishing objectivesresearch dissemination and academic evaluation for researchers, and resource support for publishers and scientific societies.",
    "In this perspective, we provide various viewpoints on alternative publication and academic evaluation models that attempt to tackle the incentive alignment problem.",
    "We encourage the scientific community to explore these and other models and to study the impact of incentive changes on researchers' behavior.",
    "Collectively, we can reshape academic publishing to better serve researchers and their scientific endeavors.",
